<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bs">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Finale</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="finale-heart">&#10084;&#65039;</div>
    <h1 class="finale-title">Stigla si do kraja!</h1>

    <span class="type-badge <%= type %>">
      <% if (type === 'emotional') { %>nježno
      <% } else if (type === 'flirty') { %>flirty
      <% } else { %>smiješno<% } %>
    </span>

    <p class="reaction"><%= response.reaction %></p>

    <div class="answer-text">
      <%= response.text %>
    </div>

    <div class="next-step" style="border-style: solid; border-color: #c9956c;">
      <h3>Hvala ti</h3>
      <p>Ova sveska je moj mali način da ti kažem koliko mi značiš. Svaka stranica, svaki QR kod, svaka riječ - sve je za tebe.</p>
      <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 12px;">Volim te.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
